= SDL_GetWindowDisplay =
Use this function to get the display index associated with a window.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetWindowDisplay(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the ,,display,, index of the display containing the center of the window on success, or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

